2026-06-18 live Discord status smoke and race hardening receipt:

- Hardened slash and prefix ingest paths to prepare the event payload, record the local `mentionId -> threadId` mapping, then post to Central Inngest. Event-send failures now leave `send_failed` records instead of disappearing after thread creation.
